Usage:

In order to run your favorite cases, set the parameters in 
    userInputs.sh and then run and plot the results by executing
    Allrun.sh and Allplot.sh scripts respectively.
    
userInputs.sh : Set the mesh, the solid models and the sampling 
    schemes;
Allrun.sh : Run the cases based on your settings in userInputs.sh;
Allplot.sh : Plot the sampled results;
Allsample-standalone.sh : In case you want only to change the 
    sampling method and not re-running the cases, execute this script.
